Single vm deployment++++++++++++++
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

First your 

>>>>>>>>>  terraform init -upgrade

then
>>>>>>>>terraform plan -out main.tfplan

then
>>>>> terraform apply "main.tfplan"


------------------------------------------

When you want to update the project 

Use 
>>>> terraform plan -out main.tfplan

After 
>>>> terraform apply "main.tfplan"


